{"tid":1424069,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院議長支持香港「反送中」示威者","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:21:04.000Z","uid":197608,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a0c32244e21cffd892318336e0e4761f1ca298e","tid":1424069,"uid":197608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國眾議院議長佩洛西發表聲明，支持香港「反送中」示威者，兩黨議員將在國會復會後，推動香港人權與民主法案。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西說入夏以來，香港人一直向全世界發出一個激動人心的訊息，就是自由、正義和民主的理想，永不會被威嚇和不公義澆滅。<br />\n<br />\n她又說香港人表現出極大勇氣，跟拒絕尊重法治、不願履行一國兩制義務的懦弱政府，形成極其鮮明的對比，香港立法會應立即徹底、並永久撤銷逃犯條例修訂工作。<br />\n<br />\n她指民主共和兩黨的國會議員將在九月，國會休會期結束後，開始推動香港人權與民主法案，為保香港民主自由和法治奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署強烈譴責佩洛西公然支持暴力抗法分子，粗暴干預香港事務和中國內政，中方對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358185&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QhVjAxyxPW1LwDR3iTeqCrKqDr4PgPuNmposci-SAQVenpxGTwY7_kks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358185%26fbclid%3DIwAR2QhVjAxyxPW1LwDR3iTeqCrKqDr4PgPuNmposci-SAQVenpxGTwY7_kks&d=JGY83BSksxqOTSpEwQoHnYpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=83a8fed5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358185%26fbclid%3DIwAR2QhVjAxyxPW1LwDR3iTeqCrKqDr4PgPuNmposci-SAQVenpxGTwY7_kks&h=37b1512b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358185&amp;fbclid=IwAR2QhVjAxyxPW1LwDR3iTeqCrKqDr4PgPuNmposci-SAQVenpxGTwY7_kks</a>"},{"pid":"4c1286877fd29c2f5a73de40dbacdf037b98fcf6","tid":1424069,"uid":197608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"香港人權與民主法 通過送哩班賣港賊 黑警歸西"}]}